"\n"
"Изберете нещо описателно, за да различавате устройствата си с един поглед — напр. „Kindle Paperwhite“ или „Kobo в хола“."

#: syncery_ui/menu/maintenance_section.lua:96
msgid ""
"A unique identifier assigned to this device when Syncery first ran.\n"
"\n"
"This ID is embedded in every sync file so other devices know which entry belongs to whom.  It is read-only — tap to see the full value or a QR code you can scan from another device."
